{
  "stem": "21310.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when we had a filled book, we would bring in the money with the stamps.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were very proud, you know, when we could fill up a book and collect, like, $5 or whatever.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That-- that was always going for Keren Kayemeth and for Palestine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my father registered.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He really wanted to go to America, and he registered for immigration in 1938, I think.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was this strict quota system.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in 19-- I think his number was supposed to come up in 1941 or '42.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were-- people were leaving, kind of, illegally to different countries.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But first of all, it did cost a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my father was very, up and very upright person, and he wouldn't do anything that wasn't very legal.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so, so we were just waiting for the quota to come.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the war fever really was quite strong at that time, you know, after the-- Czechoslovakia was evaded-- invaded, and after Austria was invaded.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Poland really knew that they were going to be next.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's when the anti-German feelings was being stirred up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all the loudspeakers and announcements on the walls of buildings proclaim '[NON-ENGLISH],' which means, 'strong, united, and ready.' But unfortunately, Poland was neither strong, not really united, nor-- nor ready.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then when the Germans invaded, it was such a complete surprise.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, all of Poland expected it, but there was-- I don't think there was any declaration of war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were just all the unrest in Gdansk, which is Danzig, because the Germans wanted that part of Poland.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's where the trouble really started.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
